text: Julia Twardowska (born Środa Wielkopolska) is a Polish female volleyball player. She is part of the Poland women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2018 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. At the club level she played for Budowlani Łódź in 2018. == References == == External links == * FIB profile * CEV profile Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Polish women's volleyball players Category:People from Środa Wielkopolska
